{"tid":1374621,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中聯辦：修訂逃犯條例提升香港法治形象","createTime":"2019-07-27T21:10:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T21:41:26.000Z","uid":50275,"like":0,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"67a207824d1eec300808bc506802049ef2016f52","tid":1374621,"uid":50275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T21:10:03.000Z","msg":"2019年5月15日 15:07<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】中聯辦指，特區政府修訂逃犯條例，有法理依據及現實迫切需要，可避免香港成為逃犯天堂，又指內地過往已向香港移交過逾二百名疑犯，但反觀香港回歸至今，未曾向內地移交犯人，修例是提升香港法治形象的重要舉措。<br />\n<br />\n中聯辦又指，基本法第95條規定，特區可與內地司法機關相互提供司法協助，修例是落實基本法應有之義，而一國兩制下，香港與內地應相互尊重、信任、支持，客觀看待及理性處理與內地、台灣及澳門等地正常司法協作關係。<br />\n<br />\n會議堅信，香港各界能拒絕和抵制別有用心的「蠱惑謠言」和「人為製造的恐慌」，相信國家在全面依法治國戰略佈局引領下的司法公正和巨大進步，共同維護香港法治核心價值，提升香港法治形象。"},{"pid":"420d999b7837ef07af28e336d7127de988856316","tid":1374621,"uid":68822,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T21:10:50.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wGX_Vgq-1G0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwGX_Vgq-1G0&d=ajJRCbjZ3CJF8zdY8%2Fu%2F15LurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=571c48f2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wGX_Vgq-1G0</a></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">【Hongkongers! Assemble! 】<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n勿忘初衷，五大訴求！</span></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">7.28  中上環 五大訴求</span></strong></ins><br />\n 1. 徹底撤回逃犯修訂條例<br />\n 2. 釋放所有因反送中被捕人士並承諾永不追究<br />\n 3. 撤回612暴動定性<br />\n 4. 追究警察濫權濫暴(包括721元朗官警黑勾結事件)，成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n 5. 立即實行雙普選"},{"pid":"1b9865e9883789aeb54e7d38f22f73a96d620f6d","tid":1374621,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T21:11:01.000Z","msg":"出5月嘅新聞到底駁咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b47ebe93bac245b7d67502949ceca568233799f5","tid":1374621,"uid":277186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T21:15:02.000Z","msg":"成篇野打臉成分好高"},{"pid":"d9b6052140a79a17606ac7f24200589f0b77d900","tid":1374621,"uid":287173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T21:41:26.000Z","msg":"聯署制裁香港政府發動元朗國家恐襲<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/sanction-hong-kong-government-its-state-terrorism-activity-conducted-yuen-long-train-station-hong-kong-721\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fsanction-hong-kong-government-its-state-terrorism-activity-conducted-yuen-long-train-station-hong-kong-721&d=ajJRCbjZ3CJF8zdY8%2Fu%2F15LurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=e1e3262d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/sanction-hong-kong-government-its-state-terrorism-activity-conducted-yuen-long-train-station-hong-kong-721</a>"}]}